reut2-007.sgm, BLOCKBUSTER ENTERTAINMENT &lt;BBEC> SELLING UNIT, Blockbuster Entertainment Corp said itwill sell its investment in Amtech Corp to the companychairman, David Cook, and president, Kenneth Anderson.    The company said the sale is taking place because Amtech isnot compatible with Blockbuster's main line of business, willrequire substaintial additional funding to develop and marketits product, and is expected to sustain operating losses forthe forseeable future.    The company said Cook and Anderson will form a new companywith the sale called Amtech Holdings Inc. Reuter&#3;
