reut2-007.sgm, COLOMBIA WILL NOT ATTEND MANAGUA COFFEE MEETING, Colombia will not attend a meeting ofcoffee producing countries scheduled for this weekend inNicaragua, Jorge Cadenas, manager of the National CoffeeGrowers' Federation, said.    We prefer to wait until things are better prepared

